<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
<title>JB Listing Analyser</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Syne:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0f0f0f;--surface:#171717;--surface2:#1e1e1e;--surface3:#252525;
  --border:#2a2a2a;--border2:#333;--text:#f0ede8;--text2:#8a8680;--text3:#505050;
  --accent:#c8f060;--accent2:#a8d040;
  --green:#4ade80;--green-bg:#0d2a1a;--green-border:#1a4a2a;
  --amber:#fbbf24;--amber-bg:#2a1f0a;--amber-border:#4a3510;
  --red:#f87171;--red-bg:#2a0f0f;--red-border:#4a1a1a;
  --blue:#60a5fa;--blue-bg:#0a1a2a;--blue-border:#1a3050;
  --r:12px;--r-sm:8px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
html,body{height:100%}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;overscroll-behavior:none}

/* ── TOP BAR ── */
.topbar{background:var(--surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 16px;height:52px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200}
.logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:-.02em;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.logo-dot{width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%}
.status-pill{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);background:var(--surface2);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.sdot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--text3);flex-shrink:0}
.sdot.on{background:var(--green)}
.sdot.pulse{animation:pulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}

/* ── BOTTOM NAV (mobile) ── */
.bottom-nav{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;z-index:200;padding-bottom:env(safe-area-inset-bottom)}
.bnav-item{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:10px 4px 8px;cursor:pointer;gap:4px;transition:color .15s}
.bnav-item .bnav-label{font-size:10px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3)}
.bnav-item .bnav-icon{font-size:18px;line-height:1}
.bnav-item.active .bnav-label{color:var(--accent)}
.bnav-item.active .bnav-icon{filter:none}
.bnav-badge{background:var(--accent);color:#0f0f0f;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;border-radius:20px;padding:1px 5px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;min-width:16px;text-align:center;position:absolute;top:6px;right:calc(50% - 18px)}
.bnav-item{position:relative}

/* ── PAGES ── */
.page{display:none;flex-direction:column;min-height:calc(100vh - 52px - 58px);padding:16px;padding-bottom:80px}
.page.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}

/* ── CARDS ── */
.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden}
.card-header{padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.card-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.card-body{padding:14px 16px}

/* ── FORMS ── */
textarea,input[type=text],input[type=url]{width:100%;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:15px;padding:12px 14px;transition:border-color .2s;-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none}
textarea{min-height:140px;resize:vertical;line-height:1.6;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px}
textarea:focus,input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent)}
textarea::placeholder,input::placeholder{color:var(--text3)}

/* ── BUTTONS ── */
.btn{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:var(--r);border:none;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;letter-spacing:.01em;-webkit-appearance:none}
.btn-accent{background:var(--accent);color:#0f0f0f}
.btn-accent:active{background:var(--accent2);transform:scale(.98)}
.btn-accent:disabled{opacity:.4;pointer-events:none}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text2);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.btn-ghost:active{background:var(--surface2)}
.btn-sm{padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;width:auto;border-radius:var(--r-sm)}
.btn-danger{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--red-border)}

/* ── LABELS ── */
.mono-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px}
.field-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:5px}

/* ── SAVED LISTING CARD ── */
.saved-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .2s;position:relative}
.saved-card:active{border-color:var(--accent)}
.saved-card-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3}
.saved-card-meta{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.5;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:2;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden}
.saved-card-footer{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.saved-card-date{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3)}
.status-badge{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500}
.badge-pending{background:var(--surface3);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.badge-promote{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);border:1px solid var(--green-border)}
.badge-caution{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber);border:1px solid var(--amber-border)}
.badge-skip{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--red-border)}
.delete-btn{position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--text3);font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;padding:4px 6px;border-radius:6px;line-height:1}
.delete-btn:active{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red)}

/* ── METRICS ── */
.metrics-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.metric-cell{background:var(--surface2);padding:12px 14px}
.metric-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:3px}
.metric-value{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);line-height:1.2}
.metric-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px}

/* ── DETAIL ROWS ── */
.detail-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);gap:12px}
.detail-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.detail-key{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);flex-shrink:0}
.detail-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);text-align:right}

/* ── VERDICT ── */
.verdict-banner{border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:14px 16px}
.vb-promote{background:var(--green-bg);border:1px solid var(--green-border)}
.vb-caution{background:var(--amber-bg);border:1px solid var(--amber-border)}
.vb-skip{background:var(--red-bg);border:1px solid var(--red-border)}
.verdict-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:5px}
.vb-promote .verdict-title{color:var(--green)}
.vb-caution .verdict-title{color:var(--amber)}
.vb-skip .verdict-title{color:var(--red)}
.verdict-body{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6}

/* ── LEAD MATCH ── */
.lead-match{border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:8px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.lead-match:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.lm-high{background:var(--green-bg);border-color:var(--green-border)}
.lm-med{background:var(--amber-bg);border-color:var(--amber-border)}
.lm-low{background:var(--red-bg);border-color:var(--red-border)}
.lm-name{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:3px}
.lm-high .lm-name{color:var(--green)}
.lm-med .lm-name{color:var(--amber)}
.lm-low .lm-name{color:var(--red)}
.lm-reason{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5}
.lm-badge{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:20px}
.lm-high .lm-badge{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);border:1px solid var(--green-border)}
.lm-med .lm-badge{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber);border:1px solid var(--amber-border)}
.lm-low .lm-badge{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);border:1px solid var(--red-border)}

/* ── PSF BAR ── */
.psf-bar-labels{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:5px}
.psf-bar-track{height:8px;background:var(--surface3);border-radius:4px;position:relative;overflow:visible}
.psf-marker{position:absolute;top:-4px;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--bg);transform:translateX(-50%)}
.psf-note{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:5px}

/* ── MARKET COMMENTARY ── */
.commentary{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);border-left:2px solid var(--accent)}

/* ── WA BOX ── */
.wa-box{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid #1a3020;border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:14px}
.wa-text{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}

/* ── PM BOX ── */
.pm-box{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:14px;border-left:2px solid var(--accent)}
.pm-text{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.9;white-space:pre-wrap}

/* ── SUCCESS TOAST ── */
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:80px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--green-bg);border:1px solid var(--green-border);color:var(--green);font-size:13px;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:600;z-index:999;opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s;pointer-events:none;white-space:nowrap}
.toast.show{opacity:1}

/* ── LEADS ── */
.lead-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:14px;margin-bottom:10px;position:relative}
.lead-card:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.lead-fields{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px}
.lead-field label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.04em;display:block;margin-bottom:3px}
.lead-field input{font-size:13px;padding:8px 10px}
.lead-field.full{grid-column:1/-1}
.remove-lead{position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;background:transparent;border:none;color:var(--text3);font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;padding:4px 6px;line-height:1;border-radius:6px}
.remove-lead:active{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red)}
.add-lead-btn{width:100%;padding:12px;background:transparent;border:1px dashed var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);color:var(--text3);font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:10px;transition:all .15s;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}
.add-lead-btn:active{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.sync-btn{width:100%;padding:11px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;transition:all .15s}
.sync-btn:active{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}

/* ── SHEET SETUP ── */
.setup-step{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;align-items:flex-start}
.step-num{min-width:24px;height:24px;background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.step-text{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6}
.step-text strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
.step-code{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px 12px;border-radius:var(--r-sm);color:var(--accent);margin-top:6px;word-break:break-all;line-height:1.8}
.alert-box{border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:12px 14px;margin:8px 0}
.alert-amber{background:var(--amber-bg);border:1px solid var(--amber-border)}
.alert-amber p{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6;margin-top:4px}
.alert-amber .alert-title{font-size:12px;color:var(--amber);font-weight:500}
.alert-blue{background:var(--blue-bg);border:1px solid var(--blue-border)}
.alert-blue p{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6;margin-top:4px}
.alert-blue .alert-title{font-size:12px;color:var(--blue);font-weight:500}

/* ── EMPTY STATE ── */
.empty{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:40px 20px;gap:10px;flex:1}
.empty-icon{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:4px}
.empty-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text2)}
.empty-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text3);max-width:220px;line-height:1.5}

/* ── LOADING ── */
.loading-bar{width:100%;height:3px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;display:none}
.loading-bar.active{display:block}
.loading-bar-fill{height:100%;background:var(--accent);animation:lb 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;width:35%}
@keyframes lb{0%{transform:translateX(-100%)}100%{transform:translateX(340%)}}
.loading-msg{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:6px;display:none}
.loading-msg.active{display:block}

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
hr{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:4px 0}

/* ── DESKTOP OVERRIDE ── */
@media(min-width:768px){
  .bottom-nav{display:none}
  .page{padding-bottom:24px;min-height:calc(100vh - 52px)}
  .desktop-nav{display:flex}
  body{font-size:14px}
  textarea{font-size:13px}
  .btn{font-size:13px;padding:11px 16px}
  .metric-value{font-size:15px}
}
@media(max-width:767px){
  .desktop-nav{display:none}
}
.desktop-nav{gap:2px;align-items:center}
.desktop-nav-item{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:var(--r-sm);font-size:12px;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text3);transition:all .15s;position:relative}
.desktop-nav-item:hover{color:var(--text2);background:var(--surface2)}
.desktop-nav-item.active{color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface2)}
.desktop-nav-badge{background:var(--accent);color:#0f0f0f;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;border-radius:20px;padding:1px 5px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-left:5px;display:inline-block}

/* ── ANALYSE MODAL (full screen on mobile) ── */
.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:300;overflow-y:auto;padding:16px;padding-bottom:32px}
.modal-overlay.open{display:block}
.modal-topbar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--bg);padding:8px 0;z-index:10}
.modal-back{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:8px 14px;color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap}
.modal-back:active{background:var(--surface2)}
.modal-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="logo"><span class="logo-dot"></span>JB Analyser</div>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px">
    <nav class="desktop-nav" id="desktop-nav">
      <div class="desktop-nav-item active" onclick="showPage('save')">Save listing</div>
      <div class="desktop-nav-item" onclick="showPage('queue')" id="dn-queue">Queue <span class="desktop-nav-badge" id="dn-badge" style="display:none"></span></div>
      <div class="desktop-nav-item" onclick="showPage('leads')">Leads</div>
      <div class="desktop-nav-item" onclick="showPage('settings')">Settings</div>
    </nav>
    <div class="status-pill"><div class="sdot pulse" id="sdot"></div><span id="stext">No sheet</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TOAST -->
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 1 — SAVE LISTING (mobile first)
     ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page active" id="page-save">
  <div>
    <div class="mono-label">Paste listing</div>
    <textarea id="listing-input" placeholder="Paste anything — WhatsApp text, portal copy, mixed language, messy format. All fine.&#10;&#10;E.g:&#10;Horizon Hills Cluster, Jln Indah 15&#10;4+1 bed 3 bath, BU 2800sqft LA 3500sqft&#10;RM780k | Freehold | Renovated&#10;OA Ahmad 012-3456789&#10;Urgent owner migrating"></textarea>
  </div>
  <button class="btn btn-accent" onclick="saveListing()">
    <span>Save to queue</span>
  </button>
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-top:-6px">Saves instantly. Analyse later when ready.</p>
</div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 2 — QUEUE
     ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="page-queue">
  <div id="queue-empty" class="empty" style="display:none">
    <div class="empty-icon">📋</div>
    <div class="empty-title">Queue is empty</div>
    <div class="empty-sub">Paste a listing on the Save tab to get started.</div>
  </div>
  <div id="queue-list" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px"></div>
</div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 3 — LEADS
     ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="page-leads">
  <div class="mono-label">Active leads</div>
  <div id="leads-list"></div>
  <button class="add-lead-btn" onclick="addLead()">+ Add lead</button>
  <button class="sync-btn" onclick="syncLeadsFromSheet()">Sync from Google Sheet</button>
  <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.5;margin-top:6px">Leads save to your browser and to the Leads tab in Google Sheet. Edit here or in the sheet — tap Sync to pull latest.</p>
</div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 4 — SETTINGS
     ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="page-settings">
  <div class="mono-label">Google Sheet</div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px">
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5">Connect your Apps Script webhook to auto-save listings and sync leads.</p>
      <input type="url" id="webhook-url" placeholder="https://script.google.com/macros/s/...">
      <button class="btn btn-accent" onclick="connectSheet()">Connect sheet</button>
      <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="showPage('setup')" style="font-size:13px;padding:10px">View setup guide</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 5 — SETUP GUIDE
     ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="page-setup">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:4px">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" onclick="showPage('settings')">← Back</button>
    <span style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700">Sheet setup guide</span>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5">One sheet, two tabs — <strong style="color:var(--text)">Listings</strong> and <strong style="color:var(--text)">Leads</strong>. Takes 5 minutes, done once.</p>

  <div class="setup-step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-text">Go to <strong>sheets.google.com</strong>, create new spreadsheet. Name it <strong>"JB Property Tracker"</strong>.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="setup-step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-text">Rename Sheet1 to <strong>Listings</strong>. Add a second tab named <strong>Leads</strong>.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="setup-step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-text">In <strong>Listings</strong> tab Row 1, add headers:
      <div class="step-code">Date | Property | Area | Price | PSF | Built Up | Land | Beds | Baths | Tenure | Furnishing | Condition | Motivation | Assessment | Gap% | Verdict | Commentary | Matched Leads | Next Action | Raw Listing</div>
